Project description

TensorBoard is a suite of web applications for inspecting and understandingyour TensorFlow runs and graphs.

Releases prior to 1.6.0 were published under the tensorflow-tensorboard nameand may be found at https://pypi.python.org/pypi/tensorflow-tensorboard.
